Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total duration of all instances of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' within the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed' versus cases leading to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' preceding it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Variation in duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across different countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Average delay introduced by 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the overall case resolution time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with more than one instance of 'Accepted + In Progress' preceding it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + In Progress occurs

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with and without 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' following it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Impact of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' on the total duration of cases ending with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that exceed the average case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Longest uninterrupted 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' period within a single case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration from start of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to any 'Completed' status activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Distribution of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' durations across different org:groups
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:group

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the fastest case to resolution versus the slowest
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases initiated by 'V30' group resources versus 'C9' group resources
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Correlation between the duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the total number of activities in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
